Full Checklist for New Cluster
On new head node:
  ✅ bash 1_setup_head_node.sh

On each new compute node:
  ✅ bash 2_setup_compute_node.sh

On new head node:
  ✅ bash 3_configure_prometheus.sh \
       --cluster-name "New-Cluster-2" \
       --region "us-east-1" \
       --ec2-ip "<ec2-elastic-ip>"

On AWS Console:
  ✅ Add new head node IP to EC2 security group port 9090

On EC2:
  ✅ Verify data arriving:
     curl -s 'http://localhost:9090/api/v1/query' \
       --data 'query={cluster="New-Cluster-2"}' | \
       python3 -m json.tool | grep '__name__' | head -5